post_text:
To honor the memory of the victims and heroes of 9/11, participate in the #DoGoodFromHome Challenge

1. Think about who you want to help and what kind act you could do for them.
2. Take a photo or video that shows you or your family making a difference from your home or in your neighborhood.
3. Post the photo/video to your social media using the #DoGoodFromHome and inspire others to take action.
4. Tag friends and ask them to join the Challenge!
5. Share the #DoGoodFromHome hashtag to unlock donations from Hasbro to benefit children of COVID-19 essential workers.

post_text: 1st grade donated the most hygiene items for the 9/11 service project with 805 toothbrushes. They have won an ice cream Popsicle party! In total, 2,659 hygiene items were donated by RMR, Aim Higher, NFL YET, AXA Advisor, and REMA New Heights Realty in South Phoenix. Thank you all for your amazing generosity as we help out homeless and needy military veterans. Lets change the world! Yes, we Can!

Pre-school & Aim Higher - Tissue Boxes

3rd Grade - Soap Bars
4th Grade - Shampoo
5th Grade - Deodorant

The last date to donate will be September 13, 2017.

Monday, August 14th we will have Volleyball tryouts for 5th – 8th grade at our NFL Yet Campus.

Tryouts start at 4:00 p.m. and end at 5:00 p.m. (tansportation between schools is unavailable)

Please come prepared in gym clothing along with the correct gym shoes and a water bottle

See Coach Natalia for any questions or concerns.

post_text: ¡Buenos trades a todos. Felicitaciones llegamos a la semifinales de la eliminatoria. (postemporada) de futbol. Tenemos entrenamiento ahora Miercloes de 4:30pm -6pm. El partido del semifinale es mañana Jueves Mayo 4 contra Sequoia a las 5:30pm. En el Campo de Legacy Traditional 14506 W. Sweetwater Ave Surprise ,AZ 85379.
